==Russian==

===Etymology===
Prefix ''[[锌褉懈-]]'', indicating action or motion towards a terminal point, and ''[[褏芯写懈褌褜]]'', to walk or go
===Verb===
'''锌褉懈褏芯写懈褌褜''' (prikhod铆t') {{impf}}, [[锌褉懈泄褌懈]] (prijt铆) {{pf}}

# to [[come]], to [[arrive]] (impf. of [[锌褉懈泄褌懈]])

